title: All-In Hold 'Em 2.1 Cards Game
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

All-In Hold &#039;Em is a version of tournament Texas Holdem poker
featuring advanced AI and high-quality graphics. Tournament
rules, including blinds, simulate tournaments such as the World
Series of Poker. Computer AI uses one of three styles of play:
loose, normal, and tight. Complete customization of the table
and cards is available. Play in career mode featuring
multi-table tournaments. 12 new computer players, a more
advanced AI with tilting and tells, career mode with multi-table
tournaments.

Version 2.1 may include unspecified updates, enhancements, or
bug fixes.
